---
// Simulator.astro - Modern two-column feature section
---
<section class="py-20 bg-autosport-navy-dark relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[linear-gradient(45deg,#ffffff_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(-45deg,#ffffff_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[length:20px_20px]"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20">
      
      <!-- Left side: Image -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative group">
        <!-- Accent glow behind image -->
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-autosport-red to-orange-500 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-autosport-navy border border-autosport-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="/images/simulator.jpg" 
            alt="Simulator auto profesional" 
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right side: Content -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-autosport-red font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3">Antrenează-te înainte de a ieși în trafic</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-text-on-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Simulator Auto Profesional</h3>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Exersează comenzile mașinii într-un simulator modern înainte de orele practice. Simulatorul te ajută să înveți controlul volanului, pedalelor și reacțiile în trafic într-un mediu sigur și controlat.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-autosport-red/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-autosport-red" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="ml-4 text-lg text-text-muted font-medium">Familiarizare rapidă cu comenzile mașinii</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-autosport-red/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-autosport-red" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="ml-4 text-lg text-text-muted font-medium">Antrenament într-un mediu sigur</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-autosport-red/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-autosport-red" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="ml-4 text-lg text-text-muted font-medium">Ideal pentru începători fără experiență</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
